IRC bot posting text based on markov chains generated from random wikipedia articles.

All files copyright (c) 2013 markfiend (AKA Mark Wolstenholme)
Released under GNU GPL v3 http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html

Except markov.py which I didn't write and is copied from 
http://agiliq.com/blog/2009/06/generating-pseudo-random-text-with-markov-chains-u/

NB the shebang line for all the python files is
#!/usr/bin/python2
This is because I'm running Arch Linux where python is a symlink to python3
